. * and what fraction of beta-having spend is tier3?
. merge m:1 category using external/betas/did_coefs, keep(1 3)

    Result                      Number of obs
    -----------------------------------------
    Not matched                        44,078
        from master                    44,078  (_merge==1)
        from using                          0  (_merge==2)

    Matched                             3,722  (_merge==3)
    -----------------------------------------

. gen has_beta = (_merge == 3)

. qui sum spend if has_beta == 1 & tier3 == 1

. di "  beta-having + tier3==1: spend=" r(sum)
  beta-having + tier3==1: spend=61958.34

. qui sum spend if has_beta == 1 & tier3 == 0

. di "  beta-having + tier3==0: spend=" r(sum)
